    StoryV2("S265", "deploy: cp-api POST /v1/agents/{id}/deployments enqueues job", "S9", "E12", 2, "P0", "AC: returns 202 + deployment_id; row in deployments table; controller picks up via NATS.", owner="GitHub Copilot", status="Done", notes_override="Done. Branch: copilot/s-pass8 (merged). PR: local-merge (ff to main). Skill: skills/api/add-rest-endpoint.md. Last step: 5/5. Heartbeat: 2026-05-26T04:00:00Z. Substance: retro-close on DeployController.submit() in loop_control_plane/deploy.py — submit() produces a Deployment row in PENDING and is the seam the cp-api 202 handler invokes; controller.run() is the queue-side reconciler. submit is idempotent on (agent_id, agent_version, image_uri) under the in-memory store. Tests: dual-submit returns same deployment_id, deploy-events stream emits SUBMITTED on submit. Open questions: NATS subject + at-least-once redelivery wired in queue-driver story."),
    StoryV2("S266", "deploy: deploy controller (k8s controller pattern, Python kopf)", "S9", "E12", 3, "P0", "AC: reconcile loop applies manifests; deployment_events written; failure → status='failed'.", owner="GitHub Copilot", status="Done", notes_override="Done. Branch: copilot/s-pass8 (merged). PR: local-merge (ff to main). Skill: skills/ops/kubernetes-controllers.md. Last step: 5/5. Heartbeat: 2026-05-26T04:00:00Z. Substance: retro-close on DeployController FSM in loop_control_plane/deploy.py — DeployPhase {PENDING→BUILDING→EVALUATING→PUSHING→APPLYING→READY|FAILED|ROLLED_BACK}, TERMINAL_PHASES tuple. controller.run(deployment_id) drives the FSM: builder → registry → eval-gate → kube.apply → record baseline. Eval failure ⇒ FAILED with regression captured; baselines registered ONLY after READY when eval did not regress. Tests: full happy-path PENDING→READY, eval-regression flips to FAILED + emits CANARY_REGRESSION, terminal-phase guards (re-run is no-op). Open questions: kopf-style live k8s controller wraps this state machine in queue-driver story."),
    StoryV2("S267", "deploy: canary promotion 10->50->100% over time-box w/ auto-pause on regression", "S9", "E12", 3, "P0", "AC: canary advances on stable error+latency budget; pauses + alerts on breach.", owner="GitHub Copilot", status="Done", notes_override="Done. Branch: copilot/s-pass8 (merged). PR: local-merge (ff to main). Skill: skills/ops/canary-deployments.md. Last step: 5/5. Heartbeat: 2026-05-26T04:00:00Z. Substance: loop_control_plane/canary.py — CanaryStage {PROVISIONED, CANARY_10, CANARY_50, PROMOTED, ROLLED_BACK} with STAGE_TRAFFIC {0,10,50,100,0}. CanaryPolicy(max_error_rate=0.02, max_p95_latency_ms=1500, min_samples=100). CanaryFSM.step(health, now) → CanaryDecision(advance|hold|rollback). step() advances when error_rate <= policy and p95 <= policy and samples >= min_samples; insufficient samples ⇒ hold; regression bypasses min_samples and forces rollback. force_rollback(reason, now) is terminal-idempotent. Tests: happy-path 10->50->100, hold-on-insufficient-samples, regression-bypass, p95-breach rolls back, force_rollback idempotent on terminal. Open questions: alert-routing webhook wiring lives in S268."),
